_sText:
An extremely balanced, tactical map that will be included in the upcoming css mod "Paintball Fun".

The first map I have released that has proper lighting and such, I have many more on the way, such as a VERY nice looking updated version of cs_nukelab.

Please enjoy!

P.S.
I specified it is indoor an outdoor as the arena is inside a building which is outside, and there is SOME stuff you can see outside but only in spectator mode, otherwise nope.

~Ando
